How to start a new branch from the latest development
-----------------------------------------------------

Procedure
---------
 1. Destroy my existing branch
    unix> git branch -D development

 2. Fetch new stuff
    unix> git fetch -a

 3. Checkout development
    unix> git checkout development

 4. Create a new branch from where I am
    unix> git checkout -b my-new-branch


    At this point, I am ready to code in my new branch


